ad3f119e11d7c4656fff8e1dd81e3bacd7a03e18:
query GetCreatedDVs @live(interval: 12000) {
  clusterCreateds(orderBy: timestamp, orderDirection: desc) {
    id
    timestamp
    txHash
    splitAddress
    eigenPodAddr
    averageAuctionScore
    winners {
      id
      nodeOp {
        nodeOpAddr
      }
      duration
      discountRate
      bidPrice
      auctionScore
      auctionType
      bidStatus
    }
    vault {
      id
      protocol
      type
      operator
      creator
      oracle
      whitelistedDeposit
      upgradeable
      timestamp
      txHash
    }
  }
}
2c7c77d328b32cc6cc73d8353368b5fbc7324d18:
query GetVaults @live(interval: 12000) {
  vaultCreateds(orderBy: timestamp, orderDirection: desc) {
    id
    protocol
    type
    operator
    creator
    oracle
    whitelistedDeposit
    upgradeable
    timestamp
    txHash
    clusters {
      id
      averageAuctionScore
      splitAddress
      eigenPodAddr
      timestamp
      txHash
      winners {
        id
        nodeOp {
          nodeOpAddr
        }
        duration
        discountRate
        bidPrice
        auctionScore
        auctionType
        bidStatus
      }
    }
  }
}
